title: Let make Google Maps even better!!!
text:
Hello people of the US using this maps! Letâ€™s help google even more better MAPS!!! 

If they send you the wrong way please take a picture and screen shot and post a review so nobody goes the wrong route again! 

Myself and people alike get lost, or are miss directed on trips and really dislike turning around! I use Google maps every time I travel so sometimes I rely on the map itself even in no service areas that it has saved me in so many ways! Just being able to see the roads like an old map! 

So please next time you get lost take a picture and post it write a review become part of this, so nobody has to get lost again! 
Hip hip. Hooray.
